A, B \in \mathbb{R}
0\leq A
0 \leq B
A \star B :=\{q\in\Bbb Q\mid q<0\}\cup\{a\cdot b\mid a\in A\wedge b\in B\wedge a\ge 0\wedge b\ge 0\}
 A, B, C \in \mathbb{R}
 C 
 A 
 B 
 C \triangleq A \cdot B 
C=\begin{cases} |A| \star |B|, & \mbox{if } (0 \leq A  \wedge  0 \leq B )\mbox{ OR }(A \leq 0 \wedge B \leq 0 )\\ -(|A| \star |B|), & \mbox{if }  (A \leq 0  \wedge  0 \leq B )\mbox{ OR } (0 \leq A  \wedge  B \leq 0 ) \end{cases}
0\cdot 0.
